quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  14,13,"Abo bangakholwayo bathi kubaProfeti babo: “Inene thina siya kunigxotha, sinikhuphe ezweni lethu kungenjalo niya kubuyela enkolweni yethu.” Ke kaloku iNkosi yabo (abaProfeti) yatyhila kubo (yathi): “Inene Thina Siza kubatshabalalisa abagabadeli.”"
  14,14,"Kananjalo Thina Siza kwenza nina ukuba ibe nini abaza kulihlala (eli) lizwe emva kwabo. Oku kokwalowo woyika ukuma phambi kwaM (ngoMhla woVuko), esoyika nesilumkiso saM.”"
  14,15,"Ke kaloku abaProfeti bafuna uloyiso noncedo eNkosini yabo (uAllâh), baza bonke abaqaqadeki nabaneenkani, nezikhukhumali ezingoozwilakhe, baba selahlekweni nasentshabalalweni"
  14,16,"Phambi kwakhe (nawuphi na osisikhukhumali somgabadeli) sisiHogo, yaye uya kwenziwa ukuba asele amanzi abilayo agxwabhazelayo"
  14,17,"Uya kuwasezwa engafuni, yaye uya kufumana ubunzima obukhulu ukuwaginya ehle ngomqala wakhe, kwaye ukufa kuya kuza kuye kuvela macala onke, kodwa akayi kufa yaye phambi kwakhe iya kuba sisohlwayo esikhulu"
  14,18,"Umzekeliso wabo bangakholwayo eNkosini yabo, kukuba imisebenzi yabo ifana nothuthu, oluvuthuzwa ngumoya ngamandla ngemini enesichotho. Abayi kukufumana oko bakusebenzelayo. Oko kukulahleka (okwababeka) kude lee (eNdleleni ethe Tye)"
  14,19,Aniboni na ukuba uAllâh Wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngenyaniso? Ethanda Anganisusa Avelise indalo entsha (esikhundleni senu)
  14,20,Kananjalo oko kuAllâh akunzimanga
  14,21,"Ke kaloku baza kuvela bonke phambi koAllâh (ngoMhla wokuGqibela); baze abo babengenamandla bathi kwabo babekhukhumele (abangabalawuli): “Inene thina sasilandela nina; ingaba ningasinceda nokuba kungantoni na ngo- kuchasene nesohlwayo sika-Allâh?” Baza kuthi bona: “Ukuba uAllâh Wayesikhokele thina, ngesasinikhokele nani. Akuyi kubakho mahluko kuthi (ngoku) nokuba singabhabhazela (ngumsindo) okanye sinyamezele (isohlwayo) ngomonde; akukho ndawo esinokuzifihla kuyo.”"